le="color: #263238; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Voucher Amount :&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #2a2c2e; font-family: Roboto-Regular, segoeui, ''HelveticaNeueLTStd Lt'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">#Amount#</span></p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><span style="color: #263238; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Please login to our Store to use the remaining balance before it&nbsp; expires.</span></p>  <p><span style="color: #263238; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Please contact our customer service for any help required!</span></p>  <p><span style="color: #263238; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Thanks and Regards,</span></p>  <p><span style="color: #263238; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">#StoreName# Support</span></p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p></body></html>',
